  subtitle:
    'Your food looks incredible in person. But your Instagram feels like stock photos, your website doesn\'t take reservations, and DMs go unanswered for hours. Meanwhile Manhattan restaurants with worse food are packed every night. Not anymore.',
  image: '/images/culture/culture-rooftop-street-team@2x.jpg',
  alt: 'Arugami team celebrating on a Hudson County rooftop',
  stats: [
    { value: '+74%', label: 'Increase in weekly covers after foundation rebuild' },
    { value: '+214%', label: 'Growth in social reach (Jersey City food collective)' },
    { value: '4.8⭐', label: 'Average rating with AI review replies' },
  ],
  primaryCta: { href: '/contact', label: 'Schedule Your Foundation Audit' },
  secondaryCta: { href: '/contact', label: 'See What We\'d Fix First' },
};

const intro =
  'Diners Google you at 6 PM, check Instagram, look at reviews, then try to book. If your website is slow, photos look dated, or nobody confirms their table—they book somewhere else. We fix the foundation FIRST—your site needs to take reservations, your Google profile needs proof, your content needs to make mouths water. THEN we deploy AI that confirms tables instantly and keeps every seat filled.';

